  "title": "如何防止手环上的个人数据丢失？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">手环本身可以保存7天数据，建议用户每天同步一次，同步到云上。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">手环可通过云服务同步保存您的个人数据。同步数据之前，请确保以下几点：1）您已安装最新的手环APP版本；2）手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接；3）手环和手机电量充足。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">请按照如下步骤同步数据：</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; \">1.     打开手环APP，点击![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084843219001.png) 进入手环设置菜单，点击“登录”，选择任一方式登录。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; \">2.     登录后，在“华为穿戴”界面下，下拉界面更新数据。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:center\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084844977002.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; \">3.     使用其他手机登录相同账号即可同步云终端数据。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal; text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\">**说明：**</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; line-height:normal; text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\">l  中途更换账号会导致数据被保存在不同的两个账号下，可能造成您的数据不一致。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; line-height:normal; text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\">l  手环电量耗尽自动关机时，若长时间放置可能会引发数据丢失，故手环低电时请及时充电。</p>",
